(182, 'Drupal Developer Required â€“ 3 Month contract - Central London', 'drupal-developer-required-aaaoe-3-month-contract-central-london__1543151365', 1, 2, 0, 0, '', '', 0, '<p><strong>Role: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Drupal Developer required &ndash; urgent.</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Rate: &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; Depends on your experience.</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Location: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Central London</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Duration: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3 month contract.</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Start Date: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ASAP.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Drupal &ndash; Excellent Technical experience &ndash; Development and Theming<br />\r\nDatabase experience &ndash; SQL &ndash; Excellent knowledge.<br />\r\nPHP ideally 5.6 &ndash; Strong Experience.<br />\r\nHTML5 and CC3 - - Web Standards &ndash; Strong Experience.<br />\r\nGood experience with client-side scripting (latest version of JavaScript, jQuery) and asynchronous web applications (AJAX / AJAJ)<br />\r\nEngine optimisation (SEO) &ndash; Good experience.<br />\r\nResponsive web design (RWD) - Good experience.</p>\r\n', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', 0, 0, 20, 0, '', 0, 0, 'Raphael Zwolinski', 1, 1, '2017-12-01', '0000-00-00', 0, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(183, 'Java / PHP development role', 'java-php-development-role__1543151365', 1, 3, 0, 0, '', '', 0, '<p>An exciting position has become available working for a leading publishing company based near Oxford, within Oxfordshire working as a Senior Application Developer. This role is also commutable from Swindon &amp; Reading.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nReporting to the Web &amp; Application Development Manager as part of the Web Infrastructure Team, you&#39;ll be tasked with Analyzing, Designing, Building and Maintaining core systems/applications for both internal and external clients as well as occasionally assisting with web development mainly using Java technologies.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou will design and build integration components and interfaces as well as provide expert tech knowledge/understanding in the modification of software for the purpose of testing based on which platform is in use.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis role is a 70/30 split in Java &amp; PHP with Java being more in use.</p>\r\n', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', 0, 0, 20, 0, '', 0, 0, 'Jamie.Bohanna', 1, 1, '2017-12-01', '0000-00-00', 0, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(184, 'Job Opportunity - Contract - Wordpress - London', 'job-opportunity-contract-wordpress-london__1543151365', 1, 2, 0, 0, '', '', 0, '<p><strong>Role:&nbsp;</strong>WordPress Developer</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Location:&nbsp;</strong>East London</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Duration:&nbsp;</strong>2 &ndash; 3 Months</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My client a mid-sized digital agency are in the market for a forward thinking WordPress Developer with the ability to modify/create new plugins. The ideal candidate will need to be able to integrate 3<sup>rd</sup>&nbsp;party API&rsquo;s and have a knowledge of Adobe Creative suite.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Skill set</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Web Technologies: HTML5/CSS3/JavaScript/JQuery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Server-side Technologies: PHP/Others a +</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Knowledge of SEO optimisation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Ability to integrate with 3rd Party API&rsquo;s</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Expert in WordPress migration and setup</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Aware of WordPress security pitfalls</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Report track and fix bugs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Experience with Git/Bitbucket</p>\r\n', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', 0, 0, 20, 0, '', 0, 0, 'Ben Sangchi', 1, 1, '2017-12-01', '0000-00-00', 0, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
