(248, 'Cornucopia - Software Engineer â€“ Milton Keynes - Permanent - Â£40,000 to Â£60,000', 'cornucopia-software-engineer-aaaoe-milton-keynes-permanent-aa40000-to-aa60000__1543151366', 1, 4, 0, 0, '', '', 0, '<p>Cornucopia is currently working with a market leading software client who currently require a software engineer to join their team in Milton Keynes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The company have an excellent reputation and are a market leader in the industries that they operate in.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My client are looking for a software engineer to develop their back end systems and support the back end code for their products. They are looking for some of the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:42pt\">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Back end development experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:42pt\">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;PHP development experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:42pt\">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;RDMS</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:42pt\">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Agile</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:42pt\">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ODD</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:42pt\">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;SQL Server</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:42pt\">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;MySQL</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:42pt\">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;No SQL</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:42pt\">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mongo</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:42pt\">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Unit testing</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:42pt\">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;TDD</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:42pt\">&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;BDD</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is a great opportunity to learn new skills in this fast paced environment.&nbsp;You could come from a C# and Java development background but want to move into back end system development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are passionate about code please reply with an up to date CV!!!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Title &ndash; Software Developer</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Salary - &pound;40,000 to &pound;60,000</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Location &ndash; Milton Keynes</p>\r\n', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', 0, 0, 20, 0, '', 0, 0, '', 2, 1, '2017-12-01', '0000-00-00', 0, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(249, 'Full Stack Video Experts', 'full-stack-video-experts__1543151366', 1, 2, 0, 0, '350', '400', 0, '<p>I have a 4 month opportunity for a video focused full stack developer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will be working on 30 video sites across several magazines. The work will be predominantly front-end focused with some aspects of PHP. You will be assisted by an ad-ops developer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The company you will be working for are a very well respected publishing client with some great names in their portfolio and the work will be done in their expansive offices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To work on this project you will need:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HTML5</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CSS3</p>\r\n\r\n<p>JavaScript (jQuery)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nice to Have:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Brightcove</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video content projects in your portfolio</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2016-08-31', '0000-00-00', 0, 58, 20, 301, 'London', 3813, 226, 'xsoka', 3, 1, '2017-12-01', '2016-06-08', 0, '', '', '', '', 'London', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(250, 'PHP DEVELOPER - FEW DAYS WORK - IMMEDIATE START PHP DEVELOPER', 'php-developer-few-days-work-immediate-start-php-developer__1543151366', 1, 2, 0, 0, '280', '300', 0, '<p>PHP Development Opportunity - Oxford - Immediate Start</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PHP Developer&nbsp;| Oxford - &pound;300 Flexible Per Day&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\nMy client is an ambitious SME with a huge development project. They would like a PHP Devleoper to come and assist for a few days with the front-end development aspects of their project. It may suit someone who is permanently employed and could work a part time project for a few days</p>\r\n', '2016-07-31', '0000-00-00', 0, 58, 20, 301, 'Oxford', 3831, 226, 'owkat', 2, 1, '2017-12-01', '2016-06-08', 0, '', '', '', '', 'Oxfordshire', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(251, 'UI Developer - Java Environment - Contract - Urgent', 'ui-developer-java-environment-contract-urgent__1543151366', 1, 2, 0, 0, '350', '400', 0, '<p>My Client are looking for a UI Developer who has got experience of working on J2EE Web Applications. We are looking for an immediate start, with interview slots available this week. The contract will be based in the East Midlands and will initially be a 3 month assignment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Essential Skills:&nbsp;<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Sound knowledge in UI technologies (JavaScript, CSS, CSS3, JQuery, Ajax, JSON, HTML5)&nbsp;<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Minimum 2+ years&rsquo; experience on J2EE based WEB Applications in a commercial environment;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Awareness of Eclipse, Ant, JBOSS;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Aware of well-known Browser computability related issues;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Aware of UI/JavaScript best practices (in terms of NFR aspects, browsers&rsquo; resource utilisation, network round-trips, etc.).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Desirable Skills:&nbsp;<br />\r\n&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Knowledge of Server-side UI technologies like Rich Faces, JSF, JSP desirable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have exclusivity on this role before other agencies for a limited amount of time so we are looking to get CV&#39;s over to the client today! Please reply with an updated copy of your CV and cofirm that you are happy to be exclusively represented for this vacancy by Oscar Associates. I in turn will make sure I contact you today and submit your CV ASAP!</p>\r\n', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', 0, 58, 20, 301, 'Midlands', 3786, 226, 'psizx', 2, 1, '2017-12-01', '2016-06-08', 0, '', '', '', '', 'East Midlands', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(252, 'Email Developer - Contract (6 Months) - Major Organisation - Central London', 'email-developer-contract-6-months-major-organisation-central-london__1543151366', 1, 2, 0, 0, '180', '200', 0, '<p>I&#39;m reaching out with with an amazing&nbsp;<strong>Email Developer role</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;working for a global Organisation based in St PAULS.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As an Email Developer you will be responsible for producing effective email marketing campaigns, which are on-brand, effective and engaging. This role will involve producing the initial concept, final artwork and HTML email builds, as well as testing and making small changes and advising on the best way to deliver templates.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Role:</strong>&nbsp;Email Developer</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Location:</strong>&nbsp;Central London</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Rate:</strong>&nbsp;&pound;180 - &pound;200</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Contract:</strong>&nbsp;6 Months<strong style=\"line-height:1.6\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Essential Experience</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Proven experience developing email marketing campaign</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Convert Photoshop comps into pixel perfect HTML layouts</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Knowledge of responsive design, cross-browser compatibility and CMS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Advanced HTML/XHTML and CSS experience (JavaScript development a plus)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Visual and UX/UI design experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Knowledge of Adobe Photoshop &amp; Dreamweaver</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Knowledge of Unica or other marketing automation tools</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Knowledge of Selligent &nbsp;or other email marketing tools</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Excellent written and verbal communication skills</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ability to work well under pressure</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Attributes</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A true passion for ECRM and how the impact it can have on Customer Experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ability to look at the bigger picture as well as deliver on the detail &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A large part of this role will involve stakeholder management due to the complexity of the customer base; the role holder must be able to demonstrate that they can work across teams.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you&#39;re interested, please reply with updated cv with availability.</p>\r\n', '2016-10-31', '0000-00-00', 0, 58, 20, 301, 'London', 3813, 226, 'ovgru', 2, 1, '2017-12-01', '2016-06-08', 0, '', '', '', '', 'London', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(253, 'Senior Freelance Designer required', 'senior-freelance-designer-required__1543151366', 1, 2, 0, 0, '200', '300', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height:1.6\">- Experience in designing for bank and financial solutions (ideal but not essential)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Must know how to visually design for mobiles and native apps as well as regular websites</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The&nbsp;deliverable is 20th August,&nbsp;<strong>to start ASAP</strong>&nbsp;(up to 9 workings days).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The goal would be to create a design direction/flavour (about 6 pages or so) for a re-design and re-brand of the bank.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please let me know ASAP if you are interested by sending over your CV and portfolio. I will then contact you with full details.</p>\r\n', '2016-08-31', '0000-00-00', 0, 58, 20, 301, 'London', 3813, 226, 'ngtza', 2, 1, '2017-12-01', '2016-06-08', 0, '', '', '', '', 'London', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(254, 'PHP Developer Contract and Perm Role - London', 'php-developer-contract-and-perm-role-london__1543151366', 1, 4, 0, 0, '45000', '65000', 0, '<p>Skill Set: PHP / MySQL / JavaScript / HTML / CSS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Exciting Opportunity for a PHP Developer with experience in PHP Programming, and ideally Magento CMS Website and Module Development, plus front end technologies like JavaScript, HTML, CSS, SASS to join a growing Specialist Magento Digital Agency based in Central London. &nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSkills&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;3-5&nbsp;years&nbsp;PHP&nbsp;experience<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;MYSQL&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;SQL&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;MVC&nbsp;Libraries&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;HTML,&nbsp;CSS,&nbsp;SASS&nbsp;/&nbsp;LESS&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Javascript,&nbsp;jQuery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please apply if this role could interest you for more details.</p>\r\n', '2016-08-31', '0000-00-00', 0, 58, 20, 301, 'London', 3813, 226, 'fhxsy', 2, 1, '2017-12-01', '2016-06-07', 0, '', '', '', '', 'London', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(255, 'Junior Web Developer - Oxon - Up to Â£20K + Benefits', 'junior-web-developer-oxon-up-to-aa20k-benefits__1543151366', 1, 3, 0, 0, '20000', '25000', 0, '<p>This is a rare opportunity to be considered as a Junior Web Developer for an award winning top fifty integrated B2B marketing agency based near Oxford with an impressive list of clients.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis is a fantastic opportunity to join a highly talented, creative and friendly team working within an exciting and unique environment on a varied range of interesting marketing campaigns, websites and digital projects.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<u><strong>Key role responsibilities:</strong></u></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Support the digital team on broad range of exciting projects, including websites, apps and email&#39;s, for a variety of clients and big brands.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Front-end website development, optimised across multiple browsers and mobile device platforms.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Contribute to the planning and development of dynamic web and digital projects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quality assurance testing of new and existing solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stay up-to-date with current web design trends and new technologies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Help to push the boundaries to produce websites and digital solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<u><strong>It is essential to have knowledge and some sort of exposure to the below to be considered for this role:</strong></u></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HTML5 and CSS3 hand-coding skills combined with knowledge of Ajax, JQuery and JavaScript.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Past exposure to&nbsp;Photoshop.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Exposure to responsive and adaptive user interfaces, Foundation or Bootstrap desirable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Knowledge of PHP and MySQL would be advantageous, but not essential.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Knowledge&nbsp;of using content management and version control systems would be advantageous.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you feel you have the necessary skills to be a part of this exciting, energetic organisation and like the idea of working with the latest technologies to better your long term career give me a call.</p>\r\n', '2016-08-31', '0000-00-00', 0, 58, 20, 301, 'Oxford', 3831, 226, 'uebqv', 2, 1, '2017-12-01', '2016-08-31', 0, '', '', '', '', 'Oxfordshire', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(256, 'Part remote Drupal Developer needed', 'part-remote-drupal-developer-needed__1543151366', 1, 4, 0, 0, '250', '325', 0, '<p>My client based near Portsmouth has an urgent requirement for a Drupal Developer an initial 3 month contract with the view to extend. &pound;250 - &pound;325pday.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>You can work part onsite and part remote. &nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>They are on lookout for both Drupal Themers and Front End Developers and separately looking for Back End Drupal Developers to work on a variety of projects, alongside some other highly skilled developers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will need to have experience with Drupal 7.</p>\r\n', '2016-09-30', '0000-00-00', 0, 58, 20, 301, 'Portsmouth ', 3798, 226, 'tkasw', 2, 1, '2017-12-01', '2016-06-07', 0, '', '', '', '', 'Hampshire', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(257, 'Software Development Team Lead - Needed!', 'software-development-team-lead-needed__1543151366', 1, 3, 0, 0, '40000', '45000', 0, '<p>I am currently working for a Cambridge based startup (moving to London) working on integrating large datasets into knowledge ontologies using machine learning techniques and perform parallelized semantic search on big data.<br />\r\nPlease see below a brief snippet of the job spec and if you are interested in progressing please forward me a copy of your updated CV.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSoftware Development Team Leader<br />\r\n&pound;40,000 - &pound;55,000 + Equity<br />\r\nJava &amp; Big Data<br />\r\nLondon<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJava/Apache Storm/Apache Spark/Natural language processing (NLP)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nClient:<br />\r\nAvanti recruiting has the pleasure of working alongside a young and exciting start up seeking a Software Development Team Lead (Java) to manage a team of software developers, two frontend and five backend as well as managing the data analyst.<br />\r\nMy client works across various fields of computer science, NLP, machine learning, graph technologies and web applications.<br />\r\nMy client&#39;s main product which you will be managing is the development of a bespoke search engine to recognise trends and predictions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMain responsibilities:<br />\r\n- To develop high quality code for complex algorithms and backend development.<br />\r\n- Plan and execute the delivery of development task according to the agile framework<br />\r\n- Manage task deliveries and within strict time deadlines<br />\r\n- Delegate work accordingly<br />\r\n- Carry out mentoring and coaching tasks<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTechnical skills:<br />\r\n- Strong leadership skills<br />\r\n- 2 years&#39; experience in development of Java<br />\r\n- Extensive server side java development<br />\r\n- Experience with JavaScript, HTML, CSS, SQL and NoSQL databases<br />\r\n- Experience of working with semantic search, graph databases and machine learning and NLP<br />\r\n- Knowledge of Apache Storm, Apache Spark, Apache Cassandra<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis role is going to be split with project/team management, quality assurance and majority development.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJava/Apache Storm/Apache Spark/Natural language processing (NLP)</p>\r\n', '2016-09-21', '0000-00-00', 0, 58, 20, 301, 'Cambridge ', 3765, 226, 'bajgo', 2, 1, '2017-12-01', '2016-06-07', 0, '', '', '', '', 'Cambridgeshire', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
