know of anyone whom it may be suitable for then please forward this on as our client is looking to interview ASAP.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please follow us on Twitter and join our LinkedIn group to hear about all the latest news and vacancies;</p>\r\n', NULL, NULL, 1, 70, 20, NULL, 'Watford', 3813, 226, 'uhagz', 1, 1, '2017-12-01', '2016-07-13', 0, '', '', '&#163; 48,000-55,000', 'ASAP', 'London', NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
