(51, 1, '360 Checkup', '360-checkup__1549191401', 1, 75, 0, 227, '1549191401xd.png', 2, 1, '2,3', '', '1', '7,9,10', '4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<p>Checkster&#39;s 360 Checkup is an automated system to provide constructive, confidential feedback for every team member in your organization. Checkster makes 360 feedback available for everyone in order to boost productivity, promote engagement in achieving company objectives, and increase job satisfaction. It is delivered online and ready to us', '<p>Checkster&#39;s 360 Checkup is an automated system to provide constructive, confidential feedback for every team member in your organization. Checkster makes 360 feedback available for everyone in order to boost productivity, promote engagement in achieving company objectives, and increase job satisfaction. It is delivered online and ready to use in minutes.</p>', 2, '2019-02-01', '2019-02-05'),
