(56, 1, 'Activeview 360', 'activeview-360__1549192060', 1, 500, 0, 227, '1549192060omj.png', 1, 1, '2', '', '1', '2,6,7,8,9,10', '5', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<p>ActiveView 360 is SurveyConnect&#39;s configurable portal to administering 360 assessments online. By using AV360 the integrity of the data is ensured, the administration process easier and more efficient, and you create a more understood and actionable output. ActiveView 360 guaranties the confidentiality of responses, therefore encouraging can', '<p>ActiveView 360 is SurveyConnect&#39;s configurable portal to administering 360 assessments online. By using AV360 the integrity of the data is ensured, the administration process easier and more efficient, and you create a more understood and actionable output. ActiveView 360 guaranties the confidentiality of responses, therefore encouraging candid feedback and meaningful results. ActiveView 360 can be customized to fit your needs and processes. Online demo and quick-quote form available!</p>', 2, '2019-02-02', '2019-02-05'),
