(138, 1, 'Cupix', 'cupix__1549218748', 1, 0, 1, 0, '15492187488r.png', 1, 3, '3', '', '1', '0', '1,2,3,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, '<p>Cupix is a SaaS app to create and share as-built VR and 3D models from photos taken by a consumer-grade 360 camera in a fully automated way. Cupix can be best used in real-estate property virtual tours or as-built visual 3D documentation of construction sites. Plus, you can compare a 3D BIM (Revit, SketchUp, IFC files) model with 360 photos side', '<p>Cupix is a SaaS app to create and share as-built VR and 3D models from photos taken by a consumer-grade 360 camera in a fully automated way. Cupix can be best used in real-estate property virtual tours or as-built visual 3D documentation of construction sites. Plus, you can compare a 3D BIM (Revit, SketchUp, IFC files) model with 360 photos side-by-side and check the differences in a very visual way. Cupix is in public beta now and anyone can sign up and start using it for free.</p>', 2, '2019-02-03', '2019-02-05'),
