(576, 1, 'Accounts Payable Software', 'accounts-payable-software__1549521018', 1, 0, 1, 0, '1549521018mou.png', 1, 8, '1,2,3', '0', '1,2', '75,77,78,79,80,81,82', '1,2,3,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, '<p>Accounts Payable functions define and supplement two very critical aspects of any business: Cash Flow and External Vendor/ Supplier Payment Management. These are directly attributable to a firm&#39;s profitability and impact each of its LOB. A systematic Accounts Payable process brings about disciplined approach to evaluate and improve Financial', '<p>Accounts Payable functions define and supplement two very critical aspects of any business: Cash Flow and External Vendor/ Supplier Payment Management. These are directly attributable to a firm&#39;s profitability and impact each of its LOB. A systematic Accounts Payable process brings about disciplined approach to evaluate and improve Financial Management for the entire organization.</p>', 1, '2019-02-07', '2019-02-07'),
