(736, 1, 'Accelo', 'accelo__1549603900', 1, 16, 0, 227, '1549603900lsb.png', 2, 13, '3', '0', '1,4,5', '124,125,126,127,128,129,130', '2,3,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '<p>As the leader in Service Operations Automation, Accelo helps over 2,000 digital &amp; creative agencies worldwide save time and become more profitable. Accelo is the all-in-one solution for agency project management and agency operations. Experience an end-to-end sales and project management solution built specifically for client-facing agencies', '<p>As the leader in Service Operations Automation, Accelo helps over 2,000 digital &amp; creative agencies worldwide save time and become more profitable. Accelo is the all-in-one solution for agency project management and agency operations. Experience an end-to-end sales and project management solution built specifically for client-facing agencies. Born out of a digital agency, Accelo knows first-hand how to make growing web companies successful.</p>', 1, '2019-02-08', '2019-02-08'),
