(738, 1, 'Wrike', 'wrike__1549604084', 1, 9, 0, 227, '154960408411g.png', 2, 13, '1,3', '0', '1,2,3,4,5', '124,125,126,127,128,129,130', '2,3,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '<p>Wrike is a work management tool for agencies that helps consolidate all your projects, communications, and files in one place, giving you the visibility you need to make sure campaigns are completed on time. You can also improve transparency and communication with clients by giving them free Collaborator seats in Wrike, so they can review assets', '<p>Wrike is a work management tool for agencies that helps consolidate all your projects, communications, and files in one place, giving you the visibility you need to make sure campaigns are completed on time. You can also improve transparency and communication with clients by giving them free Collaborator seats in Wrike, so they can review assets, check progress, and leave comments on work. Perfect for Marketing and Creative teams of 20+ people.</p>', 1, '2019-02-08', '2019-02-08'),
