(803, 1, 'Mimiro', 'mimiro__1549610662', 1, 0, 1, 0, '154961066207o.png', 1, 19, '2', '0', '1', '186,187,191,192,193,194,195', '1,2,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<p>Mimiro (www.mimiro.com), formerly ComplyAdvantage, takes a new approach to building financial crime data by providing real-time insight into the risk of people and companies globally. Broader coverage allows Mimiro to spot tens of thousands of risk events from within millions of structured and unstructured data sources, every day. Mimiros suite ', '<p>Mimiro (www.mimiro.com), formerly ComplyAdvantage, takes a new approach to building financial crime data by providing real-time insight into the risk of people and companies globally. Broader coverage allows Mimiro to spot tens of thousands of risk events from within millions of structured and unstructured data sources, every day. Mimiros suite of plug-and-play configurable cloud services seamlessly integrate to help automate and comply with Sanctions, AML and CTF regulations.</p>', 1, '2019-02-08', '2019-02-08'),
