(878, 1, 'Zoho Creator', 'zoho-creator__1549623863', 1, 15, 0, 227, '1549623863cu6.png', 2, 27, '1,2,3', '0', '1,2,3,4,5', '271,273,274,276,277,278,279,280,281,283', '1,2,3,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '<p>Zoho Creator is a cloud-based low-code application development platform that empowers you to build enterprise-class applications that run on mobile, tablet, and web. Create custom forms, configure workflows, build informative pages, and get your app up and running in minutes. Whether it&#39;s logistics or order management, the possibilities are ', '<p>Zoho Creator is a cloud-based low-code application development platform that empowers you to build enterprise-class applications that run on mobile, tablet, and web. Create custom forms, configure workflows, build informative pages, and get your app up and running in minutes. Whether it&#39;s logistics or order management, the possibilities are endless. Businesses of all sizes trust Zoho Creator to manage their data and have built more than 2 million apps on it.</p>', 1, '2019-02-08', '2019-02-08'),
(879, 1, 'Zoho Sprints', 'zoho-sprints__1549623987', 1, 12, 0, 227, '1549623987l2k.png', 1, 27, '2,3', '0', '1,4,5', '274,279,281,283', '2,3,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '<p>Zoho Sprints is a free online agile project management tool for Scrum teams. Add user stories to your backlog, estimate and prioritize work items, stay on track with personalized scrum boards and swimlanes, get actionable insights from velocity, burn up and burn down charts, collaborate with your team on a social feed, and schedule your review a', '<p>Zoho Sprints is a free online agile project management tool for Scrum teams. Add user stories to your backlog, estimate and prioritize work items, stay on track with personalized scrum boards and swimlanes, get actionable insights from velocity, burn up and burn down charts, collaborate with your team on a social feed, and schedule your review and retrospective meetings from one place.</p>', 1, '2019-02-08', '2019-02-08'),
