(1122, 1, 'Callfire', 'callfire__1549862086', 1, 5, 0, 227, '1549862086c6d.png', 2, 51, '2,3', '0', '1', '530,531,532,533,534,535,536,537,538,539', '3,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, '<p>Put your outbound dialing into overdrive with CallFire&#39;s Cloud Call Center. Simply upload your contacts, and in minutes, CallFire&#39;s Power Dialer will connect your sales agents to live leads. CallFire can call up to 4 phone lines per agent and will leave answering machine messages. CallFire saves time by weeding out busy signals, bad phon', '<p>Put your outbound dialing into overdrive with CallFire&#39;s Cloud Call Center. Simply upload your contacts, and in minutes, CallFire&#39;s Power Dialer will connect your sales agents to live leads. CallFire can call up to 4 phone lines per agent and will leave answering machine messages. CallFire saves time by weeding out busy signals, bad phone numbers, and handling answering machines. Agents focus on speaking with live customers, leading to 20-30% increases in efficiency over manual dialing.</p>', 1, '2019-02-11', '2019-02-11'),
