(1528, 1, 'Stitchex', 'stitchex__1551244139', 1, 39, 0, 227, '1551244139fb1.png', 2, 25, '3', '0', '1', '246,247,248,249,250,251,252,253,254,255,', '3,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, '<p>Stitchex is the Fashion &amp; Apparel ERP software that helps you manage all aspects of your business including sales, invoices, ordering, inventory, shipping, production, and material requirements. It comes with an online wholesale store, helping you reduce the work of managing tasks so you can focus on growing your business. It is specially de', '<p>Stitchex is the Fashion &amp; Apparel ERP software that helps you manage all aspects of your business including sales, invoices, ordering, inventory, shipping, production, and material requirements. It comes with an online wholesale store, helping you reduce the work of managing tasks so you can focus on growing your business. It is specially designed for small and medium-sized labels.</p>', 1, '2019-02-27', '2019-02-27'),
