(1530, 1, 'Apparel Connect', 'apparel-connect__1551244406', 1, 175, 0, 227, '1551244406wf6.png', 2, 25, '2,3', '0', '2', '246,247,248,249,250,251,252,253,254,255', '1,2,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, '<p>Proven, best in class, ERP solution designed specifically for garment manufacturing, Apparel Connect is typically implemented by brand owners and OEM manufacturers who have outgrown Excel and are looking for a true end to end platform to support them. Seriously comprehensive, Apparel Connect is a fully customisable solution for the entire enterp', '<p>Proven, best in class, ERP solution designed specifically for garment manufacturing, Apparel Connect is typically implemented by brand owners and OEM manufacturers who have outgrown Excel and are looking for a true end to end platform to support them. Seriously comprehensive, Apparel Connect is a fully customisable solution for the entire enterprise from Yarn Processing to Line Balancing which reduces lead times &amp; increases fabric efficiency, line efficiency, and on time performance.</p>', 1, '2019-02-27', '2019-02-27'),
