(1534, 1, 'Outfit Recommendation Software', 'outfit-recommendation-software__1551244805', 1, 0, 1, 0, '1551244805gr1.png', 1, 25, '1,2', '0', '1,2,3,4,5', '247,248,251', '1,2,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '<p>The Stylitics platform helps retailers deliver personalized, on-brand outfit recommendations to site, store, &amp; app customers to help increase average order value. Powerful, scalable, &amp; easy to use, without sacrificing quality. We work with your merchandising team to define on-brand styling guidelines, which we feed into our styling algor', '<p>The Stylitics platform helps retailers deliver personalized, on-brand outfit recommendations to site, store, &amp; app customers to help increase average order value. Powerful, scalable, &amp; easy to use, without sacrificing quality. We work with your merchandising team to define on-brand styling guidelines, which we feed into our styling algorithm. Our team of trained stylists also oversees everything, just to ensure you never receive anything other than beautiful outfits, every time.</p>', 1, '2019-02-27', '2019-02-27'),
