(1538, 1, 'Visual As/ap', 'visual-asap__1551245599', 1, 9999, 0, 227, '1551245599si.png', 1, 25, '1,2,3', '0', '2,3', '246,248,249,250,251,252,253,254,255,257,', '5', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<p>AS/AP&#39;s apparel accounting, manufacturing, and distribution software, is an integrated, modular, Windows-based system, available in Visual FoxPro or SQL Server. Complete ERP/PLM/MRP solutions, supply chain management, customer service and shop floor control. Industry-specific features include: dynamic bill-of-materials, order configurator, c', '<p>AS/AP&#39;s apparel accounting, manufacturing, and distribution software, is an integrated, modular, Windows-based system, available in Visual FoxPro or SQL Server. Complete ERP/PLM/MRP solutions, supply chain management, customer service and shop floor control. Industry-specific features include: dynamic bill-of-materials, order configurator, critical path, EDI &amp; internet solutions, SQC, intransit tracking and embellishment, email alerts, graphical planning boards, event calendars and dashboards.</p>', 1, '2019-02-27', '2019-02-27'),
(1539, 1, 'Winfashion Erp', 'winfashion-erp__1551245744', 1, 0, 1, 0, '1551245744u5z.png', 1, 25, '1,2,3', '0', '2,3,4,5', '246,247,248,250,251,252,253,254,255,256,', '1,2,3,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, '<p>We are providing Fashion ERP Software &amp; Mobile Apps We have three mobile apps, a Consumer App where the app will be submitted into the Apple app store to show your products, a iTradeshow app where you will be able take orders at the trade show to go paperless and eliminate as much data entry as possible and an iPDM app in which the Photo, de', '<p>We are providing Fashion ERP Software &amp; Mobile Apps We have three mobile apps, a Consumer App where the app will be submitted into the Apple app store to show your products, a iTradeshow app where you will be able take orders at the trade show to go paperless and eliminate as much data entry as possible and an iPDM app in which the Photo, description and style number can be automatically entered into the system via iPhone without any manual data entry.</p>', 1, '2019-02-27', '2019-02-27'),
(1540, 1, 'Axind', 'axind__1551245826', 1, 0, 1, 0, '1551245826je2.png', 1, 25, '2,3', '0', '1,2', '246,247,248,249,250,251,252,253,254,255,', '2,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, '<p>ChainReaction is a web-based suite of solutions for companies in clothing, footwear, jewelery and soft furnishings verticals. The ChainReaction suite provides seamlessly integrated products that cover your business from concept to point-of-sale. Our customers include Retailers, Wholesalers, Manufacturers, Designers, Buying Offices and Agents acr', '<p>ChainReaction is a web-based suite of solutions for companies in clothing, footwear, jewelery and soft furnishings verticals. The ChainReaction suite provides seamlessly integrated products that cover your business from concept to point-of-sale. Our customers include Retailers, Wholesalers, Manufacturers, Designers, Buying Offices and Agents across the globe. We use our expertise to create value for customers including Liz Claiborne, VF Corporation, Levis and Gruppo Coin and many more.</p>', 1, '2019-02-27', '2019-02-27'),
