(1605, 1, 'Workday Recruiting', 'workday-recruiting__1551265044', 1, 0, 1, 0, '1551265044m5k.png', 1, 26, '4', '0', '1,4,5', '261,262,263,265,266,267,268', '5', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<p>Workday Recruiting enables companies to establish and manage staffing at any level in the organization. Workday supports three different types of staffing models, so that any part of your company can be as agile or precise as it needs to function efficiently. By handling the entire lifecycle process of any worker, Workday provides a centralized ', '<p>Workday Recruiting enables companies to establish and manage staffing at any level in the organization. Workday supports three different types of staffing models, so that any part of your company can be as agile or precise as it needs to function efficiently. By handling the entire lifecycle process of any worker, Workday provides a centralized and cohesive solution to staffing and managing your global workforce.</p>', 1, '2019-02-27', '2019-02-27');
