(1665, 1, 'Jobsoid', 'jobsoid__1551330173', 1, 49, 0, 227, '1551330173fvv.png', 2, 26, '2,3', '0', '1', '259,261,262,263,265,266,267,268,269', '1,2,3', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '<p>Jobsoid is an Online Applicant Tracking System (ATS) which simplifies every step of the recruitment process in organizations, streamlining everything from sourcing potential candidates to hiring the right one. Jobsoid is an intelligent recruitment software with the ability to help save your precious time, by automatically screening candidate app', '<p>Jobsoid is an Online Applicant Tracking System (ATS) which simplifies every step of the recruitment process in organizations, streamlining everything from sourcing potential candidates to hiring the right one. Jobsoid is an intelligent recruitment software with the ability to help save your precious time, by automatically screening candidate applications and suggesting the best fit candidates for a certain job profile in your company.</p>', 1, '2019-02-28', '2019-02-28'),
