(1887, 1, 'Boomerang', 'boomerang__1551443925', 1, 195, 0, 227, '1551443925dn3.png', 2, 27, '1,2,3', '0', '2', '0', '5', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<p>Boomerang is used to improve communication with customers, suppliers, partners and employees, automate business processes and data-driven distribution of business intelligence through a wide range of pre built and powerful notification services. Boomerang helps companies around the world to build tailored notification solutions fast with an easy', '<p>Boomerang is used to improve communication with customers, suppliers, partners and employees, automate business processes and data-driven distribution of business intelligence through a wide range of pre built and powerful notification services. Boomerang helps companies around the world to build tailored notification solutions fast with an easy to use yet flexible user interface.</p>', 1, '2019-03-01', '2019-03-01'),
(1888, 1, 'Helix Core', 'helix-core__1551444036', 1, 0, 1, 0, '1551444036cqx.png', 1, 27, '2', '0', '2,3', '271,274,281,282', '1,2,3,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '<p>Helix Core is enterprise-class version control that enables faster, more collaborative development among teams independent of size or location without putting your valuable IP at risk. Helix Core boasts lightning-fast workflows, support for all file types and sizes, code review and collaboration, support for Git at scale, and a broad suite of in', '<p>Helix Core is enterprise-class version control that enables faster, more collaborative development among teams independent of size or location without putting your valuable IP at risk. Helix Core boasts lightning-fast workflows, support for all file types and sizes, code review and collaboration, support for Git at scale, and a broad suite of integrations and apps. The world&#39;s most innovative brands trust Helix Core, including Pixar, NVIDIA, Scania, EA, Ubisoft, and VMware</p>', 1, '2019-03-01', '2019-03-01'),
