(1890, 1, 'Meteor', 'meteor__1551444227', 1, 0, 1, 0, '1551444227iyq.png', 1, 27, '3', '0', '1,2,3,4,5', '0', '4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<p>Build apps that are a delight to use, faster than you ever thought possible</p>', '<p>Build apps that are a delight to use, faster than you ever thought possible</p>', 1, '2019-03-01', '2019-03-01'),
(1891, 1, 'Ultradox', 'ultradox__1551444357', 1, 29, 0, 227, '1551444357vkd.png', 2, 27, '2', '0', '1', '271,273,274,275,277,282,283', '4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '<p>With Ultradox for G Suite you can automate tedious tasks and create your own enterprise apps without hiring a team of developers. The unique combination of form builder, workflow and template engine allows you to merge, send and print documents, generate websites or send out responsive emails as part of your process. Beside automations that run ', '<p>With Ultradox for G Suite you can automate tedious tasks and create your own enterprise apps without hiring a team of developers. The unique combination of form builder, workflow and template engine allows you to merge, send and print documents, generate websites or send out responsive emails as part of your process. Beside automations that run in the background - like creating and sending out weekly reports - you can also create interactive apps like approval flows and document signing.</p>', 1, '2019-03-01', '2019-03-01'),
(1892, 1, 'Wing Python Ide', 'wing-python-ide__1551444499', 1, 0, 1, 0, '1551444499e0q.png', 1, 27, '2,3', '0', '2,3', '272,274,277,279,281,282,283', '4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '<p>Wing is a light-weight but full-featured Python IDE that uses deep code analysis to provide powerful editing, testing, and debugging capabilities. Wing offers auto-completion, call tips, auto-editing, and refactoring to speed development and reduce coding errors. Its top notch debugger works with any Python code, stored locally or on a remote ho', '<p>Wing is a light-weight but full-featured Python IDE that uses deep code analysis to provide powerful editing, testing, and debugging capabilities. Wing offers auto-completion, call tips, auto-editing, and refactoring to speed development and reduce coding errors. Its top notch debugger works with any Python code, stored locally or on a remote host. Wing also supports test-driven development, version control, UI color and layout customization, and includes extensive documentation and support.</p>', 1, '2019-03-01', '2019-03-01'),
(1893, 1, 'Ringcaptcha', 'ringcaptcha__1551444597', 1, 9, 0, 227, '1551444597ksh.png', 2, 27, '1', '0', '1', '279,281,283', '2,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, '<p>RingCaptcha is a phone identity API to onboard &#39;Real Users, Real Contact&#39; in order to build trustworthy user base &amp; provide timely communication, which is critical to businesses in sharing economy, marketplaces, fintech, cryptocurrency, e-commerce, online reservation, etc. Services include highly reliable One-Time PIN (OTP) SMS/voice', '<p>RingCaptcha is a phone identity API to onboard &#39;Real Users, Real Contact&#39; in order to build trustworthy user base &amp; provide timely communication, which is critical to businesses in sharing economy, marketplaces, fintech, cryptocurrency, e-commerce, online reservation, etc. Services include highly reliable One-Time PIN (OTP) SMS/voice/missed-call phone verification, SMS notifications, 2FA, fraud mitigation. Phone verification can be implemented with a single API call or our cut-and-paste widget.</p>', 1, '2019-03-01', '2019-03-01'),
(1894, 1, 'Joget Workflow', 'joget-workflow__1551444725', 1, 10, 0, 227, '155144472504.png', 2, 27, '1,2,3', '0', '1,2,3,4,5', '271,273,274,277,278,279,280,281,282,283', '1,2,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '<p>An open source low-code/no-code rapid application development platform, that offers full-fledged agile application development capabilities (consisting of processes, forms, lists, CRUD and UI), not just back-end EAI/orchestration/integration or the task-based interface for traditional workflow/BPM products. So for example, build a sales force au', '<p>An open source low-code/no-code rapid application development platform, that offers full-fledged agile application development capabilities (consisting of processes, forms, lists, CRUD and UI), not just back-end EAI/orchestration/integration or the task-based interface for traditional workflow/BPM products. So for example, build a sales force automation app instead of just a sales quotation approval process. Plug-in architecture, to easily extend and integrate.</p>', 1, '2019-03-01', '2019-03-01'),
(1895, 1, 'Justinmind', 'justinmind__1551444903', 1, 19, 0, 227, '1551444903zmb.png', 2, 27, '1,3', '0', '1,2,3', '279,281,283', '1,2,3,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, '<p>Justinmind is the best solution to prototype any web or mobile app you want. You can define websites and apps for Web, iOS, and Android with our intuitive drag-and-drop interface. No code involved. Just start from the template of your choice and customize it. Add our pre-loaded UI kits and give life to your design with clickable regions and link', '<p>Justinmind is the best solution to prototype any web or mobile app you want. You can define websites and apps for Web, iOS, and Android with our intuitive drag-and-drop interface. No code involved. Just start from the template of your choice and customize it. Add our pre-loaded UI kits and give life to your design with clickable regions and link interactions. Finally, test the final user experience in a click!</p>', 1, '2019-03-01', '2019-03-01'),
