(1935, 1, 'Goodbarber', 'goodbarber__1551504343', 1, 15, 0, 227, '15515043430r3.png', 2, 27, '2,3', '0', '1,4,5', '271,273,275,279', '3,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, '<p>GoodBarber is the best do-it-yourself software to create beautiful mobile projects. Used by non-developers and digital agencies, GoodBarber is a powerful tool to create the best user experience on mobile. Through a very intuitive interface, users can build and publish a Progressive Web App and a beautiful native app for iOS and Android. Leader i', '<p>GoodBarber is the best do-it-yourself software to create beautiful mobile projects. Used by non-developers and digital agencies, GoodBarber is a powerful tool to create the best user experience on mobile. Through a very intuitive interface, users can build and publish a Progressive Web App and a beautiful native app for iOS and Android. Leader in Europe and among the top 3 app builders in the world, GoodBarber is the perfect alternative to expensive bespoke mobile development projects.</p>', 1, '2019-03-02', '2019-03-02');
