(1959, 1, 'Dotconnect Ado.net Providers', 'dotconnect-adonet-providers__1551506516', 1, 99, 0, 227, '15515065161wp.png', 1, 27, '2,3', '0', '2', '271,276,281,283', '5', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '<p>dotConnect product line includes fast ADO.NET providers for MySQL, Oracle, PostgreSQL, and SQLite with support for Entity Framework, NHibernate, and LinqConnect ORM solutions and a lot of database-specific functionality, providers for DB2 and cloud apps: igCommerce, Dynamics CRM, FreshBooks, Magento, MailChimp, Salesforce, Salesforce Marketing C', '<p>dotConnect product line includes fast ADO.NET providers for MySQL, Oracle, PostgreSQL, and SQLite with support for Entity Framework, NHibernate, and LinqConnect ORM solutions and a lot of database-specific functionality, providers for DB2 and cloud apps: igCommerce, Dynamics CRM, FreshBooks, Magento, MailChimp, Salesforce, Salesforce Marketing Cloud, SugarCRM, and Zoho CRM with Entity Framework support. It also includes universal provider and provider for SQL Server.</p>', 1, '2019-03-02', '2019-03-02'),
