(2286, 1, 'Xl Release', 'xl-release__1551769072', 1, 0, 1, 0, '1551769072gbw.png', 1, 28, '1,3', '0', '2,3', '0', '1,2,3,4', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '<p>Manage the most advanced release pipelines with ease. Plan, automate and analyze the entire software release pipeline. Control and optimize software delivery. Always know the status of automated and manual steps across the release pipeline. Identify bottlenecks, reduce errors and lower the risk of release failures.</p>', '<p>Manage the most advanced release pipelines with ease. Plan, automate and analyze the entire software release pipeline. Control and optimize software delivery. Always know the status of automated and manual steps across the release pipeline. Identify bottlenecks, reduce errors and lower the risk of release failures.</p>', 1, '2019-03-05', '2019-03-05');
