(1340, 'Paypal subscription and direct payment component intergration with cakephp 3 +', 'paypal-subscription-and-direct-payment-component-intergration-with-cakephp-3__1614349525', 1, 0, 1, 'Paypal subscription and direct payment component intergration with cakephp 3 +', '<p>Hi Guys</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here we are going to discuss paypal integration. I am going to use Cakephp 3, but the same code with a few changes can be made in Cakephp 2 and 4. When you login to the skillbooker site you can down load all the code we discuss here.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am not going to discuss the paypal documentation, which means that you have to go to paypal and set up your merchant account with all the bells and whistles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So on a typical site I am going to do a few things. I am going to let the person register, then once registered, I am going to let them subscribe for a service on a website. The service has a promode which might give the person discount. The once the final price is calculated, they going to click the &#39;pay&#39; button this is going to send all the details paypal needs to paypal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The user then gets redirected to paypal to complete the transactions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once they click &#39;pay&#39; on paypal, and the transaction gets approved, paypal sends a &#39;notification&#39; which is &#39;behind the scenes&#39; but it hits our database and update it, now we know that the user has paid and there is upgraded.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When the user gets redirected back to the website, his membership is upgraded.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The paypal fields that gets send for a &#39;subscription&#39; and the just a once of payment is different.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is what gets send to paypal for a subscription:</p>\r\n<PRE>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $settings = [<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;cmd&#39; =&gt; &#39;_xclick-subscriptions&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;business&#39; =&gt; FROM_DEFAULT_EMAIL,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;item_name&#39; =&gt; $salesoption-&gt;name,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;item_number&#39; =&gt; $salesoption-&gt;id, &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;currency_code&#39; =&gt; &#39;USD&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;a3&#39; =&gt; $salesoption-&gt;discounted,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; //&#39;a3&#39; =&gt; $salesoption-&gt;price,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;p3&#39; =&gt; &#39;1&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;t3&#39; =&gt; &#39;Y&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;src&#39; =&gt; 1,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;srt&#39; =&gt; 52,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;sra&#39; =&gt; 1,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;return_url&#39; =&gt; DOMAIN.&#39;/payments/paypalreturn&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;cancel_url&#39; =&gt; DOMAIN.&#39;/payments/paypalcancel&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;notify_url&#39; =&gt; DOMAIN.&#39;/payments/notify&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;custom&#39; =&gt; $custom<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ];</p>\r\n</PRE>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is what get send to paypal for just a payment:</p>\r\n<PRE>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $settings = [<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;cmd&#39; =&gt; &#39;_xclick&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;business&#39; =&gt; FROM_DEFAULT_EMAIL,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;lc&#39; =&gt; &#39;US&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;item_name&#39; =&gt; $salesoptions-&gt;name,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;item_number&#39; =&gt; $salesoptions-&gt;id,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;amount&#39; =&gt; $salesoptions-&gt;price,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;currency_code&#39; =&gt; &#39;USD&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;button_subtype&#39; =&gt; &#39;services&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;no_note&#39; =&gt; &#39;0&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;tax_rate&#39; =&gt; &#39;0.000&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;shipping&#39; =&gt; &#39;0.00&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;bn&#39; =&gt; &#39;PP-BuyNowBF:btn_buynowCC_LG.gif:NonHostedGuest&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;first_name&#39; =&gt; $this-&gt;Auth-&gt;user(&#39;firstname&#39;),<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;last_name&#39; =&gt; $this-&gt;Auth-&gt;user(&#39;lastname&#39;),<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;payer_email&#39; =&gt; $this-&gt;Auth-&gt;user(&#39;email&#39;),<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;return_url&#39; =&gt; DOMAIN.&#39;/payments/paypalreturn&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;cancel_url&#39; =&gt; DOMAIN.&#39;/payments/paypalcancel&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;notify_url&#39; =&gt; DOMAIN.&#39;/payments/notify&#39;,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &#39;custom&#39; =&gt; $custom<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ];</p>\r\n</PRE>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will see in the code that I leave all the debug code in. The only way to debug this properly is to write what you get back from paypal to a log file. Because the &#39;notifications&#39; happen behing the scenes, you can not debug it on the screen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The the fields paypal returned for subscription and for payment is also dfferent.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are the fields that are returned for subscription:</p>\r\n<PRE>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;amount3 = $data[&#39;amount3&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;address_status = $data[&#39;address_status&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;recur_times = $data[&#39;recur_times&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;subscr_date = $data[&#39;subscr_date&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;payer_id = $data[&#39;payer_id&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;address_street = $data[&#39;address_street&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;mc_amount3 = $data[&#39;mc_amount3&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;address_zip = $data[&#39;address_zip&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;first_name = $data[&#39;first_name&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;reattempt = $data[&#39;reattempt&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;address_country_code = $data[&#39;address_country_code&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;address_name = $data[&#39;address_name&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;subscr_id = $data[&#39;subscr_id&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;custom = $data[&#39;custom&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;payer_status = $data[&#39;payer_status&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;business = $data[&#39;business&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;address_country = $data[&#39;address_country&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;address_city = $data[&#39;address_city&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;verify_sign = $data[&#39;verify_sign&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;payer_email = $data[&#39;payer_email&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;payer_business_name = $data[&#39;payer_business_name&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;last_name = $data[&#39;last_name&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;address_state = $data[&#39;address_state&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;receiver_email = $data[&#39;receiver_email&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;recurring = $data[&#39;recurring&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;txn_type = $data[&#39;txn_type&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;item_name = $data[&#39;item_name&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;mc_currency = $data[&#39;mc_currency&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;item_number = $data[&#39;item_number&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;residence_country = $data[&#39;residence_country&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;period3 = $data[&#39;period3&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;ipn_track_id = $data[&#39;ipn_track_id&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $raw-&gt;createdtime = date(&quot;Y-m-d H:i:s&quot;);<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $tablep-&gt;save($raw);</p>\r\n</PRE>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are the fields returned for a once off payment:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<PRE>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $receive-&gt;txnid = $data[&#39;txn_id&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $receive-&gt;item_name = $data[&#39;item_name&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $receive-&gt;item_number = $data[&#39;item_number&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $receive-&gt;payment_amount = $data[&#39;payment_amount&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $receive-&gt;payment_status = $data[&#39;payment_status&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $receive-&gt;payment_currency = $data[&#39;payment_currency&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $receive-&gt;receiver_email = $data[&#39;receiver_email&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $receive-&gt;payer_email = $data[&#39;payer_email&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $receive-&gt;custom = $data[&#39;custom&#39;];<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $receive-&gt;user_id = $awardeduser;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $receive-&gt;awardeduser = $awardeduser;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $receive-&gt;payuser = $user_id;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $receive-&gt;source = $source;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $receive-&gt;project_id = $project_id;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $receive-&gt;stage = $stage;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $receive-&gt;createdtime = date(&quot;Y-m-d H:i:s&quot;);</p>\r\n</PRE>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'gabriel kolbe', 'VgD99XHoveA', 'paypalintegration.zip', 7430, '2021-02-26', '2022-01-24');
